   <description>Set brush for drawing filled areas.</description>
   <discussion>
SET_BRUSH() sets the fill color of any of the functions that draw an enclosed area, such as  RECT()and OVAL(). 
Limitations: Used only in the Code sections of UI_BITMAP_DRAW(), UI_SCREEN_DRAW(), and UI_PRINTER_DRAW().
   </discussion>
